{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hides this view unconditionally."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hidden","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A hidden view."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Hidden views are invisible and can’t receive or respond to interactions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, they do remain in the view hierarchy and affect layout. Use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this modifier if you want to include a view for layout purposes, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"don’t want it to display.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["HStack {","    Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        .hidden()","    Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third circle takes up space, because it’s still present, but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenSwiftUI doesn’t draw it onscreen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"type":"paragraph","inli